    "note": "Every shipping field carries an integration_status. A 'source-integrated' field is bound to the shared controller-driven regex builder and MUST have a matching entry in regex-search-integrations.json (the checker reconciles the two registries and fails closed on drift). A 'gap' field is an honest, still-unintegrated surface; it MUST carry a gap_category from the fixed enum below plus non-empty gap_evidence citing a real file:symbol anchor for the architectural reason it cannot yet reuse the builder. Existing upstream (non-Material-guarded) source never satisfies the integration gate, so gap_evidence documents WHY, it is not a passing integration.",
